[[cdo:11 nguŏk 3 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[zh-min-nan:11 goe̍h 3 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh-yue:十一月初三]] {{Lunisolar November}} '''November 3''' is the 3rd day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November|12=draft}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft}} and its day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft}} {{ill|592|ja|592|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Soga no Umako|ja|蘇我馬子|12=draft}} had Emperor {{ill|Sushun Tennō|ja|崇峻天皇|12=draft}} assassinated.
