{{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 15th shōgun of the Muromachi shogunate († {{ill|1597|ja|1597|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 16th year ({{ill|8=ja|9=閏|Intercalation (timekeeping)|lt=Intercalation|kk= (timekeeping)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1639|ja|1639|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 27|ja|12月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an astronomer († {{ill|1715|ja|1715|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1836|ja|1836|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Murata Shinpachi|ja|村田新八|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1877|ja|1877|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1841|ja|1841|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tanaka Shōzō|ja|田中正造|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a member of the House of Representatives and social reformer († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1854|ja|1854|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takamine Jōkichi|ja|高峰譲吉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a pharmacologist († {{ill|1922|ja|1922|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|592|ja|592|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – Emperor {{ill|Sushun Tennō|ja|崇峻天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 32nd emperor.
