== Deaths == * {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|592|ja|592|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – Emperor {{ill|Sushun Tennō|ja|崇峻天皇|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 32nd emperor.
