{{Lunisolar November}} '''November 3''' is the 3rd day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} and its day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝}} . == Events == * {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|592|ja|592}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日}} ) – {{ill|Soga no Umako|ja|蘇我馬子}} had Emperor {{ill|Sushun Tennō|ja|崇峻天皇}} assassinated. == Births == * {{ill|Daiei|ja|大永}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1521|ja|1521}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日}} ) – {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|Takeda Shingen}} , a warlord († {{ill|1573|ja|1573}} ). * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|1537|ja|1537}} {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|Ashikaga Yoshiaki}} , the 15th shōgun of the Muromachi shogunate († {{ill|1597|ja|1597}} ). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永}} 16th year ({{ill|8=ja|9=閏|Intercalation (timekeeping)|lt=Intercalation|kk= (timekeeping)}} ) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1639|ja|1639}} {{ill|December 27|ja|12月27日}} ) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海}} , an astronomer († {{ill|1715|ja|1715}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1836|ja|1836}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日}} ) – {{ill|Murata Shinpachi|ja|村田新八}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1877|ja|1877}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保}} 12th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1841|ja|1841}} {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日}} ) – {{ill|Tanaka Shōzō|ja|田中正造}} , a member of the House of Representatives and social reformer († {{ill|1913|ja|1913}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1854|ja|1854}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日}} ) – {{ill|Takamine Jōkichi|ja|高峰譲吉}} , a pharmacologist († {{ill|1922|ja|1922}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} {{ill|592|ja|592}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日}} ) – Emperor {{ill|Sushun Tennō|ja|崇峻天皇}} , the 32nd emperor.
