{{Lunisolar November}} 
'''November 3''' is the 3rd day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)}}  – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}}  and its day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝}} .
== Events ==
* {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}}  {{ill|592|ja|592}}  {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日}} ) – {{ill|Soga no Umako|ja|蘇我馬子}}  had Emperor {{ill|Sushun Tennō|ja|崇峻天皇}}  assassinated.
