2=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|Takeda Shingen|qq=|12=draft}} , a warlord († {{ill|1573|ja|1573|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1537|ja|1537|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|qq=|12=draft}} , the 15th shōgun of the Muromachi shogunate († {{ill|1597|ja|1597|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}} 16th year ({{ill|8=ja|9=閏|Intercalation (timekeeping)|lt=Intercalation|kk= (timekeeping)|qq=|12=draft}} ) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1639|ja|1639|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 27|ja|12月27日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|qq=|12=draft}} , an astronomer († {{ill|1715|ja|1715|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1836|ja|1836|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Murata Shinpachi|ja|村田新八|qq=|12=draft}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1877|ja|1877|qq=|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft}} 12th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1841|ja|1841|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 15|ja|12月1