q=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|Takeda Shingen|qq=|qq=draft}} , a warlord († {{ill|1573|ja|1573|qq=|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1537|ja|1537|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|qq=|qq=draft}} , the 15th shōgun of the Muromachi shogunate († {{ill|1597|ja|1597|qq=|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft}} 16th year ({{ill|8=ja|9=閏|Intercalation (timekeeping)|lt=Intercalation|kk= (timekeeping)|qq=|qq=draft}} ) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1639|ja|1639|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 27|ja|12月27日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|qq=|qq=draft}} , an astronomer († {{ill|1715|ja|1715|qq=|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1836|ja|1836|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Murata Shinpachi|ja|村田新八|qq=|qq=draft}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1877|ja|1877|qq=|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft}} 12th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1841|ja|1841|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tanaka Shōzō|ja|田中正造|qq=|qq=draft}} , a member of the House of Representatives and social reformer († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|qq=|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1854|ja|1854|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Takamine Jōkichi|ja|高峰譲吉|qq=|qq=draft}} , a pharmacologist († {{ill|1922|ja|1922|qq=|qq=draft}} ).
