{{Not to be confused with|November 3|qq=November 3}}[[Category:Days of the Japanese Lunisolar Calendar]]<!--why is this category always showing up as 347 members?--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十一月初三|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 11월 3일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 3''' is the 3rd day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} and its day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senshō|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suiko Tennō|qq=}} 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|592|ja|592|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/592|qq=}} [[:en:December 12|December 12]] ) – [[:en:Soga no Umako|Soga no Umako]] had Emperor [[:en:Emperor Sushun|Sushun Tennō]] assassinated. == Births == * [[:en:Daiei (era)|Daiei]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1521|ja|1521|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1521|qq=}} [[:en:December 1|December 1]] ) – {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|Takeda Shingen|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Shingen|qq=}} , a warlord († {{ill|1573|ja|1573|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1573|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmon (era)|qq=}} 6th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1537|ja|1537|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1537|qq=}} [[:en:December 5|December 5]] ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Yoshiaki|qq=}} , the 15th shōgun of the Muromachi shogunate († {{ill|1597|ja|1597|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1597|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 16th year ([[:en:Intercalation (timekeeping)|Intercalation]] ) ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1639|ja|1639|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1639|qq=}} [[:en:December 27|December 27]] ) – [[:en:Shibukawa Shunkai|Shibukawa Harumi]] , an astronomer († {{ill|1715|ja|1715|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1715|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 7th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1836|ja|1836|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1836|qq=}} [[:en:December 10|December 10]] ) – {{ill|Murata Shinpachi|ja|村田新八|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Murata Shinpachi|qq=}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1877|ja|1877|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1877|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 12th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1841|ja|1841|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1841|qq=}} [[:en:December 15|December 15]] ) – [[:en:Shōzō Tanaka|Tanaka Shōzō]] , a member of the House of Representatives and social reformer († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1913|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1854|ja|1854|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1854|qq=}} [[:en:December 22|December 22]] ) – [[:en:Takamine Jōkichi|Takamine Jōkichi]] , a pharmacologist († {{ill|1922|ja|1922|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1922|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suiko Tennō|qq=}} 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|592|ja|592|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/592|qq=}} [[:en:December 12|December 12]] ) – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Sushun|Sushun Tennō]] , the 32nd emperor.
