n:December 1|December 1]] ) – {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|Takeda Shingen|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Shingen|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} , a warlord († [[:en:1573|1573]] ). * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmon (era)|qq=}} 6th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1537|1537]] [[:en:December 5|December 5]] ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|ja|Ashikaga Yoshiaki|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Yoshiaki|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} , the 15th shōgun of the Muromachi shogunate († [[:en:1597|1597]] ). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 16th year ([[:en:Intercalation (timekeeping)|Intercalation]] ) ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1639|1639]] [[:en:December 27|December 27]] ) – [[:en:Shibukawa Shunkai|Shibukawa Harumi]] , an astronomer († [[:en:1715|1715]] ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 7th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1836|ja|1836|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1836|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:December 10|December 10]] ) – {{ill|Murata Shinpachi|ja|村田新八|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Murata Shinpachi|qq=}} , a Satsuma retainer and politician († {{ill|1877|ja|1877|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1877|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 12th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1841|ja|1841|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1841|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:December 15|December 15]] ) – [[:en:Shōzō Tanaka|Tanaka Shōzō]] , a member of the House of Representatives and social reformer († {{ill|1913|ja|1913|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1913|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} ). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1854|ja|1854|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1854|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:December 22|December 22]] ) – [[:en:Takamine Jōkic